{"tid":616525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 在職婦女懷孕要跟「更表」　比上司早懷孕是自私行為","createTime":"2018-04-04T08:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T13:39:21.000Z","uid":55851,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3273988069ab63245369f73d78b17fca767f05d2","tid":616525,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/4/1522788761_xb-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F4%2F1522788761_xb-1280w.jpg&h=b566d9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本部分公司被揭有一項潛規則，視乎女性員工職位的高低，決定她們結婚生子的時間，如返工般要輪「更表」。愛知縣一名託兒所女員工因比上司早懷孕，而被指責自私，其丈夫在《每日新聞》撰文稱妻子不按「更表」而意外懷孕，為此感不安，甚至要向上司道歉。另有一名在東京從事化妝品行業的已婚女店員稱，被上司警告35歲才可懷孕。有評論斥此規則違反人權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/日在職婦女懷孕要跟「更表」-121445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%B7%E5%A9%A6%E5%A5%B3%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E8%A6%81%E8%B7%9F%E3%80%8C%E6%9B%B4%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%8D-121445&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaSzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=ccf4654b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/日在職婦女懷孕要跟「更表」-121445</a>"},{"pid":"f116c173233acef9e001baddf3415d700f4f6f70","tid":616525,"uid":20658,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"on9國家"},{"pid":"7d9f47ff10931c09d5dc4de876d612430061e779","tid":616525,"uid":113626,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"係香港<br />\n你大肚係公司基本上係打橫行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7701a39c937de898fb12d9d8650ee53ca057f06b","tid":616525,"uid":76216,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"政府一定出聲屌  <br />\n人口已經不足  <br />\n哩D古怪文化更阻礙日本人口增長"},{"pid":"6995e61af5c8e3cb79fbcda631302165f10c4349","tid":616525,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"